About the Hackathon
#BUIDL your own path, Shape your own Web3 Journey!
The #BUIDL for Web3 Hack (2022) is designed to open up access to the Web3 space for #BUIDLers like you. Based on your skill level, we invite you to choose a track featured by a Web3 platform that best suits your project.
#BUIDL & Win Big!

Developer Support (FAQ)

How many people can be on a team?

You can form teams of up to 5 people. You can team up with hackers of any country or experience level! Join the Lumos Metaverse Discord Server

I'm new to Web3. Can I participate?

Yes, you can participate in the #BUIDL for Web3 Hack. We will be providing you with a Hackathon Kit, which will include all the necessary tools to participate in the Hackathon. You can also participate in the Hackathon by following the instructions in the Hackathon Kit.

Is the #BUIDL for Web3 Hack (2022), a team hackathon or an individual one?

The #BUIDL for Web3 Hack is a team hackathon. You can form teams of up to 5 people. You can team up with hackers of any country or experience level! Join the Lumos Metaverse Discord Server.

Can I make an individual submission?

Yes, you can submit your own project. You can also submit your project to the Lumos Metaverse Discord Server.

Who owns the IP to my project?

You own the IP

What is the selection criteria for #BUIDL for Web3 Hack (2022)?

The selection criteria for #BUIDL for Web3 Hack (2022)

Does #BUILD for Web3 Hack provide any Career Opportunities?

Yes, #BUILD for Web3 Hack provides Career Opportunities for the participants.

To access ongoing work Opportunities, Join our recruitment channel
